            <lg xml:id="TK93">
<l>mukattā ṉamarntiṉitu nōkki yakattāṉu</l>
<l>miṉco liṉatē yaṟam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sweet words said sweetly looking with cheerful mien and with</l>
<l>true mind—this is dharma.</l>
